<https://haulaah.github.io/CIRPO/courseofaction/41144_detection_1> a :CourseOfAction ;
    a :Detection ;
    :hasCoaDescription "=== TASK ACTIVITY HISTORY ===  --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~40988920 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 14:56 Type: case_task_log Message: SOC detected multiple high-severity alerts indicating malicious activity. Alerts include suspicious executables in Temp directories, encoded PowerShell commands, outbound connections to suspicious domains and unusual authentication activity. Shortly after alerts began, users reported encrypted files with .df_locked extension on srv-web01.irorg.local.    --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~24696 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:02 Type: case_task_log Message: Evidence:  SIEM Alerts  User Reports Endpoint protection alerts" ;
    :hasCoaStatus "Completed" ;
    :hasCoaCreationDateTime "2026-02-24T14:50"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaStartDateTime "2026-02-24T14:56"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaEndDateTime "2026-02-24T14:58"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaCreationAnalyst [ a :Analyst ; :hasAnalystEmail "responder4@irorg.com" ] ;
    :hasCoaAssignedAnalyst [ a :Analyst ; :hasAnalystEmail "responder4@irorg.com" ] ;
.

<https://haulaah.github.io/CIRPO/courseofaction/41144_containment_1> a :CourseOfAction ;
    a :Containment ;
    :hasCoaDescription "=== TASK ACTIVITY HISTORY ===  --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~94392 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:30 Type: case_task_log Message: Network isolation: * ws-user03 * ws-user04  * srv-web01 * srv-bakcup01  IP blocks: * 142.93.122.23 (suspicious)  Account actions  * 1. Disable admin_ir * 2. Reset Privileged passwords  Block the domains * servicewikii.com * onixcellent.com * chishir.com * qw.balanarr.com * vc.myobtain.com   --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~40984648 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:24 Type: case_task_log Message: Containment measures   1. Isolate ws-user03, ws-user0 and srv-backup01 from the network 2. Disable admin_ir credentials  3. Disconnect srv-web01 from network 4. Apply firewall blocks for malicious IPs and domains" ;
    :hasCoaStatus "Completed" ;
    :hasCoaCreationDateTime "2026-02-24T14:50"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaStartDateTime "2026-02-24T15:24"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaEndDateTime "2026-02-24T15:31"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaCreationAnalyst [ a :Analyst ; :hasAnalystEmail "responder4@irorg.com" ] ;
    :hasCoaAssignedAnalyst [ a :Analyst ; :hasAnalystEmail "responder4@irorg.com" ] ;
.

