    :hasCoaDescription "=== TASK ACTIVITY HISTORY ===  --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~41021688 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:33 Type: case_task_log Message: Remove Malware from infected systems and reset domain admin credentials   Delete: * update_213.exe * svchost32.exe * credscan.exe * df.exe  Reset:  * All domain admin accounts * Service accounts * User passwords" ;
