<https://haulaah.github.io/CIRPO/courseofaction/41144_analysis_1> a :CourseOfAction ;
    a :Analysis ;
    :hasCoaDescription "=== TASK ACTIVITY HISTORY ===  --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~41042024 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:09 Type: case_task_log Message: Attack timeline  9:12 Dropper binary executed on user workstation (ws-user03) 9:13 Connection attempt to suspected C2 domain (servicewikii.com) 9:13 Suspicious PowerShell script executed from user workstation 9:16 Secondary loader / Beacon module executed (ws-user04) 9:17 Outbound traffic to external beacon server 9:18 Windows event log cleared  9:21 Suspicious admin login originating from workstation (dc01.irorg.local) 9:24 Outbound connection to suspected C2 / Beacon Server 9:26 Encryption module executed and initiated (host=srv-web01.irorg.local) 9:31 Outbound connection from backup server to external host   --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~28712 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:15 Type: case_task_log Message: Summary  Investigation identified ws-user03.irorg.local as potential initial infection host via execution of update_213.exe from TEMP directory.  Lateral movement occurred to ws-user04.irorg.local and to dc01.irorg.local using admin credentials.   df.exe was executed on the server serv-web01.irorg.local resulting in widespread file encryption.    --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~110776 Author: responder3@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:51 Type: case_task_log Message: Ryuk ransomware UNC1878 threat actor BazarBackdoor TrickBot / Anchor malware Healthcare-sector ransomware campaigns" ;
    :hasCoaStatus "Completed" ;
    :hasCoaCreationDateTime "2026-02-24T14:50"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaStartDateTime "2026-02-24T15:09"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaEndDateTime "2026-02-24T15:19"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasCoaCreationAnalyst [ a :Analyst ; :hasAnalystEmail "responder4@irorg.com" ] ;
    :hasCoaAssignedAnalyst [ a :Analyst ; :hasAnalystEmail "responder4@irorg.com" ] ;
.

<https://haulaah.github.io/CIRPO/courseofaction/41144_postincidentactivity_1> a :CourseOfAction ;
    a :PostIncidentActivity ;
    :hasCoaDescription "=== TASK ACTIVITY HISTORY ===  --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~49192 Author: responder4@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:48 Type: case_task_log Message: Incident review identified possible compromise via malicious executable in TEMP directory likely delivered through phishing as there is a correlated event with the same IP 88.119.174.129  Lessons Learned  * Users able to execute files from TEMP * Admin account reused on workstation  Improvements * Block execution from TEMP  * Network Segregation    --- LOG ENTRY --- ID: ~65752 Author: responder3@irorg.com Date: 24/02/2026 15:51 Type: case_task_log Message: Ryuk ransomware UNC1878 threat actor BazarBackdoor TrickBot / Anchor malware Healthcare-sector ransomware campaigns" ;
